  "elapsed_s": 1.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that procession was-- it was advisable for one's own safety to wait 5 or 10 minutes in a doorway of a house, or go inside the doorway of the house, and wait 'til the procession went, because the whole atmosphere was created-- you Jews killed our God and this is the time of the year and you are responsible for it.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Now needless to say, not every member of a community-- of a city are intelligent, normal-thinking people and bigotry takes roots very quickly.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, the more uneducated ruffians took heed of the priest's words.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if I may transgress a long period of time, because this point I very much would like to make.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In 1946, after the war, after all what had happened, I lived in the town of my grandparents with my uncles in Szombathely, which was well known to me, because I was the only survivor in my family.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I clearly remember that the Hungarian Primate, whose name is Mindszenty, was internationally known because he took refuge in the 1956 revolution in the American embassy for 15 years, made a speech in Hungarian, in the main square-- Fo ter it was called, I can give you practically the date in 1946-- in which he went on to say, I cannot understand all the commotion which is being created that so many Jews got killed.",
      "word_count": 75
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After all, there was a war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Many Hungarians got killed in many other nations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Maybe a somewhat larger percentage got killed, but I'm not aware of anything serious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, I think this is the cause of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
